        "primary": {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "The First Emirati Luxury Department Store Reimagined",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "HOB marked the UAE’s first Emirati luxury department store, and this Yas Mall flagship was a pivotal moment in elevating its identity. The store was envisioned as a premium multi-brand destination — housing perfumes, fashion, accessories, jewelry, and private event spaces — designed to reflect global luxury standards while remaining rooted in regional identity.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
